---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
import InfoCard from "@components/InfoCard.astro";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import createSlug from "../lib/createSlug";

const posts = (await getCollection("blog")).sort(
  (a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf(),
);

const last_posts = posts.slice(0, 3);
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
  <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">Are You Ready? üî•</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">
      The Algo-rhythmic Chase Begins!
    </div>
    <div class="text-xl py-1">January 4 - 7th, 2025 <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> "Anywhere on Earth"</div>
    <hr class="my-4" />
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
Iris returns to take you to an exciting algorithmic voyage this winter. With over <b>1000+ registrations</b> pouring in our last two editions, the excitement was palpable and the competition more fierce. Be ready to ignite your passion for programming, artificial intelligence and machine learning once again.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
The beauty of LogicLoom lies in its accessibility. Mentoring sessions are provided to support participants in navigating the challenges, ensuring that everyone has the opportunity to excel regardless of their background. Participants also avail the opportunity to foster their spirit of teamwork and versatility in tackling various challenges as the competition unfolds. The stage is set, the challenges await - let's soar to new heights together and make it a booming success once againnnn üí•
</text>
    </div>
  
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i> Announcements</div>

    <div class="divider my-0"></div>

    <InfoCard
      title="Registration"
      img="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/6857/6857461.png"
      sub="Contest, Workshop"
      desc="Registration is live at margazhi.iitmparadox.org"
      url="/register"
      badge="NEW"
      target="_self"
    />

    <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">What's in store for this Winter <i class="fa fa-bomb" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="AlgoX Compete"
    img="https://d2908q01vomqb2.cloudfront.net/c5b76da3e608d34edb07244cd9b875ee86906328/2021/08/04/AdobeStock_203293749.jpeg"
    desc="A Machine Learning contest tackling a challenging real-world NLP problem. This isn't just another hackathon, we celebrate ML here. Participants will truly understand the essence once they join us."
    url="/rules"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Workshops"
    img="/workshop.png"
    desc="Whether you're new to the field or already have some understanding, these sessions led by top experts from academia and industry will offer an immersive learning experience, packed with industry insights and practical knowledge."
    url="/speakers"
    loading="lazy"
  />

    <div class="py-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Past Winners üèÜ</div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-8">
            
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-400 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Margazhi 2024</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-black mt-2">Gobalakrishnan V, Debasmit M, Jayandra L</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-400 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Paradox 2024</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-black mt-2">Derrick Samuel R, Marri Bhuvan, Harsh Kumar</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center bg-yellow-400 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-crown text-4xl text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Margazhi 2025</div>
                    <div class="text-lg text-black mt-2">Who knows, it can be YOU!! üòè</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="py-8">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">What People Are Saying üí¨</div>

        <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="feedback-carousel overflow-hidden">

                <!-- Feedback Item 1 -->
                <div class="feedback-item text-center p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-xl font-semibold">"Attempted many technical events in various editions of Paradox. LogicLooM tops them all. Good support, amazing coordination and overall an excellent event. Kudos to the organizers. Will be looking forward to future events."</div>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">- GK</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feedback Item 2 -->
                <div class="feedback-item text-center p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-xl font-semibold">"Warmup questions were like jalebi:) They wrapped around twisting it multiple times. Round2 was hard! We scratched our head for 2.5 hours and did what we could. In this process, we definitely learnt a lot. Thanks to LogicLooM team for organizing such a great event. Had too much fun and learning."</div>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">- Siddharth</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feedback Item 3 -->
                <div class="feedback-item text-center p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <div class="text-xl font-semibold">"The event was so great and well structured that a newbie in ML like me was also able to make a ML model and even get a descent
                score, building my confidence in the first try. Also, the organizers have also managed the event very well."</div>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">- Krish, Md. Shah</div>
                </div>

            <!-- Prev and Next buttons -->
            <button class="prev-btn absolute top-1/2 left-0 transform -translate-y-1/2 bg-yellow-500 text-white p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400">
                <i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i>
            </button>
            <button class="next-btn absolute top-1/2 right-0 transform -translate-y-1/2 bg-yellow-500 text-white p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400">
                <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 mt-15">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="divider">Supported By</div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10 mt-2 md:justify-around"
      >
        <div class="text-gray-400 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow flex gap-4 items-center">
          <a href="https://www.iitmparadox.org/" target="_blank"><Image
            src="/paradox_logo.png"
            width={150}
            height={150}
            format="webp"
            alt="paradox margazhi logo"
            class="max-w-full md:max-w-[10rem] rounded-lg"
          /></a>
<!--<a href="https://wayanad.iitmbs.org" target="_blank"><Image
            src="https://wayanadiitm.github.io/ml/events/logicloom2/storage/whouse.PNG"
            width={150}
            height={150}
            format="png"
            alt="wayanad house logo"
            class="max-w-full md:max-w-[5rem] rounded-lg"
          /></a>-->
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
